    "start": 3.136,
    "duration": 1.101
  },
  {
    "text": "that we have not seen before.",
    "start": 4.237,
    "duration": 2.002
  },
  {
    "text": "Slamming what he calls the,",
    "start": 6.239,
    "duration": 1.502
  },
  {
    "text": "quote, bizarre",
    "start": 7.741,
    "duration": 1.034
  },
  {
    "text": "and quote",
    "start": 8.775,
    "duration": 0.667
  },
  {
    "text": "ridiculous allegations",
    "start": 9.442,
    "duration": 1.235
  },
  {
    "text": "Trump made against him",
    "start": 10.677,
    "duration": 0.967
  },
  {
    "text": "in the Oval Office",
    "start": 11.644,
    "duration": 0.868
  },
  {
    "text": "just hours ago.",
    "start": 12.512,
    "duration": 0.901
  },
  {
    "text": "So here's",
    "start": 13.413,
    "duration": 0.667
  },
  {
    "text": "some of what Trump said.",
    "start": 14.08,
    "duration": 2.803
  },
  {
    "text": "The witchhunt",
    "start": 16.883,
    "duration": 0.501
  },
  {
    "text": "that you should",
    "start": 17.384,
    "duration": 0.467
  },
  {
    "text": "be talking about",
    "start": 17.851,
    "duration": 1.201
  },
  {
    "text": "is they, quote, President Obama",
    "start": 19.052,
    "duration": 1.635
  },
  {
    "text": "absolutely called",
    "start": 20.687,
    "duration": 1.535
  },
  {
    "text": "Tulsi Gabbard.",
    "start": 22.222,
    "duration": 2.269
  },
  {
    "text": "what they did to this country",
    "start": 24.491,
    "duration": 1.635
  },
  {
    "text": "in 2016, starting in 2016.",
    "start": 26.126,
    "duration": 3.036
  },
  {
    "text": "But going up all the way,",
    "start": 29.162,
    "duration": 1.335
  },
  {
    "text": "going up to 2020.",
    "start": 30.497,
    "duration": 1.701
  },
  {
    "text": "In the election,",
    "start": 32.198,
    "duration": 1.268
  },
  {
    "text": "they tried to rig the election.",
    "start": 33.466,
    "duration": 1.502
  },
  {
    "text": "We found",
    "start": 34.968,
    "duration": 1.334
  },
  {
    "text": "this isn't like evidence",
    "start": 36.302,
    "duration": 1.569
  },
  {
    "text": "or that this is like proof,",
    "start": 37.871,
    "duration": 2.302
  },
  {
    "text": "irrefutable proof",
    "start": 40.173,
    "duration": 1.702
  },
  {
    "text": "that Obama was seditious.",
    "start": 41.875,
    "duration": 3.236
  },
  {
    "text": "That Obama",
    "start": 45.512,
    "duration": 2.335
  },
  {
    "text": "was trying to lead a coup.",
    "start": 47.847,
    "duration": 3.003
  },
  {
    "text": "All right.",
    "start": 51.051,
    "duration": 0.2
  },
  {
    "text": "Trying to lead a coup.",
    "start": 51.251,
    "duration": 0.901
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, usually",
    "start": 52.152,
    "duration": 1.268
  },
  {
    "text": "anyone associated with Obama",
    "start": 53.42,
    "duration": 1.201
  },
  {
    "text": "just just ignores all that.",
    "start": 54.621,
    "duration": 1.601
  },
  {
    "text": "They don't respond.",
    "start": 56.222,
    "duration": 0.801
  },
  {
    "text": "But that is not",
    "start": 57.023,
    "duration": 0.834
  },
  {
    "text": "what happened this time.",
    "start": 57.857,
    "duration": 1.569
  },
  {
    "text": "Obama's spokesperson",
    "start": 59.426,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "responded in part,",
    "start": 60.427,
    "duration": 1.601
  },
  {
    "text": "and I quote, ",
    "start": 62.028,
    "duration": 1.335
  },
  {
    "text": "Jamal Simmons is OutFront",
    "start": 77.377,
    "duration": 1.034
  },
  {
    "text": "now, and the former Republican",
    "start": 78.411,
    "duration": 1.669
  },
  {
    "text": "governor of Minnesota,",
    "start": 80.08,
    "duration": 0.7
  },
  {
    "text": "Tim Pawlenty.",
    "start": 80.78,
    "duration": 0.668
  },
  {
    "text": "All right.",
    "start": 81.448,
    "duration": 0.2
  },
  {
    "text": "I appreciate both of you",
    "start": 81.648,
    "duration": 1.368
  },
  {
    "text": "very much.",
    "start": 83.016,
    "duration": 0.7
  },
  {
    "text": "So, Jamal, look,",
    "start": 83.716,
    "duration": 1.235
  },
  {
    "text": "this is a change",
    "start": 84.951,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "to come from Team Obama.",
    "start": 85.952,
    "duration": 1.902
  },
  {
    "text": "It's a spokesperson, okay?",
    "start": 87.854,
    "duration": 1.134
  },
  {
    "text": "But it's a change.",
    "start": 88.988,
    "duration": 1.035
  },
  {
    "text": "And to come out",
    "start": 90.023,
    "duration": 0.734
  },
  {
    "text": "and to speak like that,",
    "start": 90.757,
    "duration": 1.168
  },
  {
    "text": "bizarre allegations",
    "start": 91.925,
    "duration": 1.401
  },
  {
    "text": "are ridiculous",
    "start": 93.326,
    "duration": 0.834
  },
  {
    "text": "and a weak attempt",
    "start": 94.16,
    "duration": 0.701
  },
  {
    "text": "at distraction.",
    "start": 94.861,
    "duration": 0.968
  },
  {
    "text": "now, Trump said",
    "start": 96.796,
    "duration": 0.668
  },
  {
    "text": "that Obama",
    "start": 97.464,
    "duration": 0.467
  },
  {
    "text": "is trying to stage a coup,",
    "start": 97.931,
    "duration": 0.967
  },
  {
    "text": "so that's what caused this.",
    "start": 98.898,
    "duration": 1.602
  },
  {
    "text": "But, what do you think?",
    "start": 100.5,
    "duration": 2.669
  },
  {
    "text": "How significant of a departure",
    "start": 103.169,
    "duration": 1.201
  },
  {
    "text": "is this for",
    "start": 104.37,
    "duration": 0.634
  },
  {
    "text": "for Obama",
    "start": 105.004,
    "duration": 0.568
  },
  {
    "text": "to actually say, okay,",
    "start": 105.572,
    "duration": 0.867
  },
  {
    "text": "we're going to respond?",
    "start": 106.439,
    "duration": 2.403
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, first of all, it's",
    "start": 108.842,
    "duration": 0.533
  },
  {
    "text": "pretty rich that the man",
    "start": 109.375,
    "duration": 1.068
  },
  {
    "text": "who is sort of affiliated",
    "start": 110.443,
    "duration": 1.068
  },
  {
    "text": "with the January 6th",
    "start": 111.511,
    "duration": 1.034
  },
  {
    "text": "insurrection",
    "start": 112.545,
    "duration": 0.901
  },
  {
    "text": "at the Capitol",
    "start": 113.446,
    "duration": 0.734
  },
  {
    "text": "is the one accusing people",
    "start": 114.18,
    "duration": 0.968
  },
  {
    "text": "of trying to stage a coup.",
    "start": 115.148,
    "duration": 1.868
  },
  {
    "text": "you know, Obama about a,",
    "start": 117.016,
    "duration": 1.769
  },
  {
    "text": "you know, a few days ago",
    "start": 118.785,
    "duration": 1.368
  },
  {
    "text": "came out",
    "start": 120.153,
    "duration": 0.567
  },
  {
    "text": "and went after Democrats",
    "start": 120.72,
    "duration": 1.168
  },
  {
    "text": "and said,",
    "start": 121.888,
    "duration": 0.4
  },
  {
    "text": "you know,",
    "start": 122.288,
    "duration": 0.234
  },
  {
    "text": "it's time for Democrats to be,",
    "start": 122.522,
    "duration": 1.969
  },
  {
    "text": "you know, to speak up and to,",
    "start": 124.491,
    "duration": 1.801
  },
  {
    "text": "you know, not do so much",
    "start": 126.292,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "navel gazing.",
    "start": 127.293,
    "duration": 0.968
  },
  {
    "text": "You know,",
    "start": 128.261,
    "duration": 0.167
  },
  {
    "text": "he did that at a fundraiser.",
    "start": 128.428,
    "duration": 1.068
  },
  {
    "text": "And so",
    "start": 129.496,
    "duration": 0.6
  },
  {
    "text": "I think a lot of Democrats",
    "start": 130.096,
    "duration": 1.101
  },
  {
    "text": "said, well,",
    "start": 131.197,
    "duration": 0.534
  },
  {
    "text": "a lot of people",
    "start": 131.731,
    "duration": 0.701
  },
  {
    "text": "are speaking up.",
    "start": 132.432,
    "duration": 0.767
  },
  {
    "text": "They're marching,",
    "start": 133.199,
    "duration": 0.634
  },
  {
    "text": "they're stepping up.",
    "start": 133.833,
    "duration": 0.734
  },
  {
    "text": "And where are you",
    "start": 134.567,
    "duration": 1.168
  },
  {
    "text": "at, President Obama?",
    "start": 135.735,
    "duration": 0.868
  },
  {
    "text": "And so now I think we see",
    "start": 136.603,
    "duration": 0.934
  },
  {
    "text": "President Obama stepping up to.",
    "start": 137.537,
    "duration": 1.602
  },
  {
    "text": "And so he's stepping up",
    "start": 139.139,
    "duration": 1.201
  },
  {
    "text": "and saying something",
    "start": 140.34,
    "duration": 0.7
  },
  {
    "text": "to the American public.",
    "start": 141.04,
    "duration": 0.968
  },
  {
    "text": "He refuses to sit back",
    "start": 142.008,
    "duration": 1.602
  },
  {
    "text": "and allow Donald Trump",
    "start": 143.61,
    "duration": 0.901
  },
  {
    "text": "to accuse him",
    "start": 144.511,
    "duration": 0.667
  },
  {
    "text": "of leading a coup.",
    "start": 145.178,
    "duration": 0.834
  },
  {
    "text": "And remember,",
    "start": 146.012,
    "duration": 0.534
  },
  {
    "text": "it wasn't just what he said,",
    "start": 146.546,
    "duration": 1.168
  },
  {
    "text": "Trump said in the Oval Office.",
    "start": 147.714,
    "duration": 1.568
  },
  {
    "text": "President Trump said",
    "start": 149.282,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "he also released a video",
    "start": 150.283,
    "duration": 2.502
  },
  {
    "text": "on his social media network",
    "start": 152.785,
    "duration": 1.802
  },
  {
    "text": "showing Barack Obama",
    "start": 154.587,
    "duration": 1.468
  },
  {
    "text": "being arrested",
    "start": 156.055,
    "duration": 0.768
  },
  {
    "text": "in the Oval Office.",
    "start": 156.823,
    "duration": 0.834
  },
  {
    "text": "And that generated",
    "start": 157.657,
    "duration": 1.435
  },
  {
    "text": "video, right? Yeah, yeah.",
    "start": 159.092,
    "duration": 2.636
  },
  {
    "text": "And maybe that was part of what",
    "start": 161.728,
    "duration": 1.435
  },
  {
    "text": "what prompted",
    "start": 163.163,
    "duration": 0.667
  },
  {
    "text": "the actual response here?",
    "start": 163.83,
    "duration": 2.035
  },
  {
    "text": "it is it is it is a change.",
    "start": 165.865,
    "duration": 2.169
  },
  {
    "text": "All right.",
    "start": 168.034,
    "duration": 0.3
  },
  {
    "text": "And it's a change coming from,",
    "start": 168.334,
    "duration": 2.303
  },
  {
    "text": "the former president.",
    "start": 170.637,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "So it matters in that respect.",
    "start": 171.638,
    "duration": 1.768
  },
  {
    "text": "Governor Pawlenty.",
    "start": 173.406,
    "duration": 0.868
  },
  {
    "text": "Speaker Johnson is now saying",
    "start": 174.274,
    "duration": 2.102
  },
  {
    "text": "that he would not be opposed",
    "start": 176.376,
    "duration": 1.134
  },
  {
    "text": "to subpoenaing Obama",
    "start": 177.51,
    "duration": 1.568
  },
  {
    "text": "to testify before",
    "start": 179.078,
    "duration": 1.268
  },
  {
    "text": "Congress over",
    "start": 180.346,
    "duration": 0.734
  },
  {
    "text": "these allegations. Here he is.",
    "start": 181.08,
    "duration": 1.602
  },
  {
    "text": "We have no concern about that.",
    "start": 185.018,
    "duration": 1.268
  },
  {
    "text": "If it's uncomfortable for him,",
    "start": 186.286,
    "duration": 1.301
  },
  {
    "text": "he shouldn't",
    "start": 187.587,
    "duration": 0.3
  },
  {
    "text": "have been involved in",
    "start": 187.887,
    "duration": 1.068
  },
  {
    "text": "in overseeing this,",
    "start": 188.955,
    "duration": 1.134
  },
  {
    "text": "which is what it appears",
    "start": 190.089,
    "duration": 0.935
  },
  {
    "text": "to us has happened.",
    "start": 191.024,
    "duration": 1.968
  },
  {
    "text": "there's a lot of",
    "start": 192.992,
    "duration": 0.601
  },
  {
    "text": "allegations on the table.",
    "start": 193.593,
    "duration": 1.301
  },
  {
    "text": "Our job is to go",
    "start": 194.894,
    "duration": 1.135
  },
  {
    "text": "and follow each of those trials",
    "start": 196.029,
    "duration": 1.401
  },
  {
    "text": "and to find out the truth.",
    "start": 197.43,
    "duration": 3.003
  },
  {
    "text": "obviously that's coming",
    "start": 202.435,
    "duration": 1.135
  },
  {
    "text": "in the context of, of",
    "start": 203.57,
    "duration": 1.267
  },
  {
    "text": "of the",
    "start": 204.837,
    "duration": 0.501
  },
  {
    "text": "the changing of the topic",
    "start": 205.338,
    "duration": 1.368
  },
  {
    "text": "going on in Washington,",
    "start": 206.706,
    "duration": 2.035
  },
  {
    "text": "especially with Johnson away",
    "start": 208.741,
    "duration": 1.302
  },
  {
    "text": "from Epstein.",
    "start": 210.043,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "But, governor, I'm",
    "start": 211.044,
    "duration": 0.667
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm curious as to",
    "start": 211.711,
    "duration": 1.401
  },
  {
    "text": "whether you think Obama now",
    "start": 213.112,
    "duration": 2.67
  },
  {
    "text": "now taking a sharper tone",
    "start": 215.782,
    "duration": 1.568
  },
  {
    "text": "and stepping up",
    "start": 217.35,
    "duration": 0.601
  },
  {
    "text": "as opposed to",
    "start": 217.951,
    "duration": 0.6
  },
  {
    "text": "to being quiet",
    "start": 218.551,
    "duration": 1.035
  },
  {
    "text": "and trying to take the high",
    "start": 219.586,
    "duration": 1.635
  },
  {
    "text": "road.",
    "start": 221.221,
    "duration": 0.867
  },
  {
    "text": "Is it too little, too late,",
    "start": 222.088,
    "duration": 1.168
  },
  {
    "text": "or does it matter",
    "start": 223.256,
    "duration": 0.734
  },
  {
    "text": "for Democrats?",
    "start": 223.99,
    "duration": 3.003
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, of course, former",
    "start": 227.26,
    "duration": 0.667
  },
  {
    "text": "governors, former presidents",
    "start": 227.927,
    "duration": 1.235
  },
  {
    "text": "always try to be",
    "start": 229.162,
    "duration": 0.801
  },
  {
    "text": "a little measured as to when",
    "start": 229.963,
    "duration": 1.201
  },
  {
    "text": "and how they respond",
    "start": 231.164,
    "duration": 1.034
  },
  {
    "text": "to their successors.",
    "start": 232.198,
    "duration": 1.268
  },
  {
    "text": "President Obama",
    "start": 233.466,
    "duration": 0.768
  },
  {
    "text": "has been pretty muted",
    "start": 234.234,
    "duration": 1.034
  },
  {
    "text": "in that regard,",
    "start": 235.268,
    "duration": 0.834
  },
  {
    "text": "with a few exceptions.",
    "start": 236.102,
    "duration": 1.301
  },
  {
    "text": "But in this case, President",
    "start": 237.403,
    "duration": 1.135
  },
  {
    "text": "Trump called him out directly,",
    "start": 238.538,
    "duration": 1.668
  },
  {
    "text": "and President",
    "start": 240.206,
    "duration": 0.534
  },
  {
    "text": "Obama answered the bell",
    "start": 240.74,
    "duration": 1.034
  },
  {
    "text": "and swung back.",
    "start": 241.774,
    "duration": 2.002
  },
  {
    "text": "Aaron, like you,",
    "start": 243.776,
    "duration": 0.768
  },
  {
    "text": "I read the Mueller report.",
    "start": 244.544,
    "duration": 1.334
  },
  {
    "text": "It basically concluded",
    "start": 245.878,
    "duration": 1.235
  },
  {
    "text": "that the Russians did",
    "start": 247.113,
    "duration": 0.934
  },
  {
    "text": "try to interfere",
    "start": 248.047,
    "duration": 0.834
  },
  {
    "text": "with the election,",
    "start": 248.881,
    "duration": 0.634
  },
  {
    "text": "but there was no actual proof",
    "start": 249.515,
    "duration": 1.335
  },
  {
    "text": "of coordination in that regard.",
    "start": 250.85,
    "duration": 2.102
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm not aware, nor",
    "start": 252.952,
    "duration": 0.968
  },
  {
    "text": "have I seen any",
    "start": 253.92,
    "duration": 0.6
  },
  {
    "text": "public reporting,",
    "start": 254.52,
    "duration": 0.901
  },
  {
    "text": "that President Obama",
    "start": 255.421,
    "duration": 1.502
  },
  {
    "text": "somehow ordered",
    "start": 256.923,
    "duration": 1.535
  },
  {
    "text": "something inappropriate",
    "start": 258.458,
    "duration": 1.401
  },
  {
    "text": "relative to that investigation.",
    "start": 259.859,
    "duration": 1.435
  },
  {
    "text": "If Tulsi Gabbard",
    "start": 261.294,
    "duration": 0.867
  },
  {
    "text": "or the president",
    "start": 262.161,
    "duration": 0.668
  },
  {
    "text": "President Trump",
    "start": 262.829,
    "duration": 0.634
  },
  {
    "text": "has that kind of evidence,",
    "start": 263.463,
    "duration": 1.535
  },
  {
    "text": "then they should",
    "start": 264.998,
    "duration": 0.467
  },
  {
    "text": "bring it forward.",
    "start": 265.465,
    "duration": 0.6
  },
  {
    "text": "Otherwise, this is",
    "start": 266.065,
    "duration": 1.101
  },
  {
    "text": "seems like puffery.",
    "start": 267.166,
    "duration": 1.635
  },
  {
    "text": "Right. Well, absolutely.",
    "start": 268.801,
    "duration": 2.102
